Python-General purpose Programming Language

Py - comments are non executable statements.
Identifer Rules
Name in python program - Identifer
variable name
function name
class name


Identifer Rules
----------------
1.Identifier should contains only: a-z/ A-Z/ 0-9/_
2.Identifier should not start with digits: 0-9
3.Idenfifier should not contains any special char/symbols
4.Should not use keyword as identifer
5.Idenfiers are case-sensitive

