int data type:
---------------------------

List - DS
---------
group of elements/values/objects as one entity
allowed duplicats
allowed heterogenous elements
list elements are storing based on indexing(0 to n-1)
-ve indexing and +ve indexing
insertion order maintained
list is mutable object
list is iterable object(for loop and while loop)

================================================

Tuple - DS
---------
group of elements/values/objects as one entity
allowed duplicats
allowed heterogenous elements
Tuple elements are storing based on indexing(0 to n-1)
-ve indexing and +ve indexing
insertion order maintained
Tuple is Immmutable object
Tuple is iterable object(for loop and while loop)

Tuple is Read only of List.

========================================
List is Mutable
Tuple is Immutable Object.

set - Datastructure
------------------------
group of elements/values/objects as one entity
duplicates are not allowed
Heterogenous elements are allowed
indexing concept is not applicable.
Set is mutable object.
set - we can iterate using only for loop.

